-- Troika Dialog Names Anatoly Popov Head of Retail Operations
-- B y   B r a d   C o o k
-- 2012-04-20T07:10:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-20/troika-dialog-names-anatoly-popov-head-of-retail-operations.html
Troika Dialog,  Russia ’s oldest
investment bank, said it named Anatoly Popov as head of the
company’s retail business.  “One of Popov’s main tasks will be the gradual integration
of Troika Dialog’s distribution network into Sberbank’s retail
arm,” Troika said in a statement today. OAO Sberbank, Russia’s
largest lender, controls Troika. Popov will continue to be a
vice president at state-run Sberbank.  To contact the reporter on this story:
